{"tid":1257419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 若明天立法會不能開會港府將割地給解放軍起軍事碼頭","createTime":"2019-06-25T14:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T14:12:30.000Z","uid":110895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc94dff203e196866f0b9354535f9ebc2ac385cb","tid":1257419,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:10:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ctseng.love.hotdog/posts/10206492386864047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fctseng.love.hotdog%2Fposts%2F10206492386864047&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=4686a236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ctseng.love.hotdog/posts/10206492386864047</a><br />\n如果明天立法會無法開會, 保護地方令將會於6月29日自動生效<br />\n<br />\n明天立法會議程:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/counmtg/agenda/cm20190626.htm?fbclid=IwAR163zZV9VaGeisKeKV5KB1foQ2VLpf4GhQAziouh9yHhICm3CaoKXuLSOo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fagenda%2Fcm20190626.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR163zZV9VaGeisKeKV5KB1foQ2VLpf4GhQAziouh9yHhICm3CaoKXuLSOo&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=f31b196e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/counmtg/agenda/cm20190626.htm?fbclid=IwAR163zZV9VaGeisKeKV5KB1foQ2VLpf4GhQAziouh9yHhICm3CaoKXuLSOo</a><br />\n<br />\nCLS...睇少一眼都出事<br />\n班狗官全部割脈啦<br />\n做咩割香港人啲地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02efff500940cd65fbb9c8f414d9cfde0120b52e","tid":1257419,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"中環海濱長廊一幅 0.3 公頃土地，被政府改劃為「軍事用地」。本周三（26日）立法會大會將審議相關的附屬法例，議會陣線朱凱迪和區諾軒提出多項修訂，包括是將附屬法例廢除等。保護海濱聯盟今日發出緊急呼籲，要求全體立法會議員支持廢除議案，避免將中環海濱「送中」。<br />\n<br />\n立法會星期三將會討論中區軍用碼頭相關的附屬法例，區諾軒將提出多項修訂要求廢除附屬法例。朱凱迪則提出將生效日期由本月底，推遲至明年、後年或2047年。<br />\n<br />\n保護海濱聯盟今日指，政府有關做法等同將中環海濱「送中」，指港人的海濱公共空間慘變成軍事用地，是嚴重損害公眾利益。聯盟呼籲全體立法會議員支持廢除議案，不要強行通過惡法、製造社會矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n2014 年城規會決定將中環海濱長廊核心地段之 150 米長、3,000 平方米面積的土地劃作「軍事用途」。分區計劃大綱圖於今年 1 月已提交予特首林鄭月娥，她同意了計劃草案並於 2 月 1 日刊憲關於批准計劃草案的通知。<br />\n<br />\n今年 2 月，立法會議員朱凱廸與中環海濱關注組名名成員到中環海濱長廊集會，抗議政府長廊用地劃作軍事用途，供駐港解放軍使用。朱凱廸批評，政府不單不取回閒置軍事用地作公共用途，更將現有公共空間改劃為軍事用地，要求政府立即開放該處用地予公眾，只有解放軍需要停泊船隻時才暫時圍封。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月保安局亦在立法會保安事務委員會提交文件，指政府計劃於本立法年度內，提交法例修訂建議予立法會，並於立法工作完成後，將碼頭正式移交予駐軍。<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n講得唔夠詳細...<br />\n以上轉自立場新聞:<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%89%B2%E8%AE%93%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D-%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E4%BF%83%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%88/?fbclid=IwAR18f5CILVJrrYmwCA8fXstOXINg4WZxrzkzQ1txkoOGMaSChkc1aIfLY4o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25BF%25B1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2589%25B2%25E8%25AE%2593%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25BF%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E9%2599%25A4%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%25A1%2588%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR18f5CILVJrrYmwCA8fXstOXINg4WZxrzkzQ1txkoOGMaSChkc1aIfLY4o&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=e06c26dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25BF%25B1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2589%25B2%25E8%25AE%2593%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25BF%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E9%2599%25A4%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%25A1%2588%2F%3